{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">This suffix is used to ask quantitative questions like &ldquo;How big?&rdquo; &ldquo;How heavy?&rdquo; and so forth. It is placed directly after the short form of the adjective:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྗི་པོ་</span> &ldquo;Heavy,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྗི་ལོས་</span> &ldquo;How heavy?&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆེན་པོ་</span> &ldquo;Big,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆེ་ལོས་</span> &ldquo;How big?&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐག་རིང་པོ་</span> &ldquo;Far,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐག་རིང་ལོས་</span> &ldquo;How far?&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>","title":""}]}